---
title: HelloHero: Double Spiced Beef & Jewel Couscous with Yoghurt & Almonds
description: Couscous — the grain so nice they named it twice! Here we’ve added sweet currants and nutty almonds for a pop of flavour, and topped the whole thing off with mildly spiced beef strips and greens. Don’t forget a generous dollop of cooling yoghurt to bring the meal together.

